# =========================================================
# SUPER_ADMIN Permission Testing
# ตาม SRS: SUPER_ADMIN ทำได้เฉพาะ
# 1. ตั้งค่าระบบ (System Configuration)
# 2. ดูรายงานทั้งหมด (View All Reports)
# ❌ ไม่สามารถ CRUD Incident/Store/Equipment ได้
# =========================================================

### ===============================================
### STEP 1: Login as Super Admin
### ===============================================
POST {{apiBase}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "superadmin@rim.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

# หลังจาก run แล้ว:
# Copy access_token ทั้งหมดจาก response
# Paste ลงในบรรทัดที่ 5 (@tokenSuperAdmin = ...)

### ===============================================
### STEP 2: SUPER_ADMIN View Equipment (Should Success ✅)
### ===============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/equipment
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenSuperAdmin}}

# Expected: 200 OK ✅
# SUPER_ADMIN สามารถดูรายงานได้

### ===============================================
### STEP 3: SUPER_ADMIN View Equipment by ID (Should Success ✅)
### ===============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/equipment/19
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenSuperAdmin}}

# Expected: 200 OK ✅
# SUPER_ADMIN สามารถดูรายละเอียดได้

### ===============================================
### STEP 4: SUPER_ADMIN View Statistics (Should Success ✅)
### ===============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/equipment/19/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenSuperAdmin}}

# Expected: 200 OK ✅
# SUPER_ADMIN สามารถดูสถิติได้

### ===============================================
### STEP 5: SUPER_ADMIN View Logs (Should Success ✅)
### ===============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/equipment/19/logs?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenSuperAdmin}}

# Expected: 200 OK ✅
# SUPER_ADMIN สามารถดู logs ได้

### ===============================================
### STEP 6: SUPER_ADMIN Create Equipment (Should Fail ❌)
### ===============================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/equipment
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenSuperAdmin}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serialNumber": "SN-SUPERADMIN-FAIL",
  "name": "Super Admin Should Not Create",
  "category": "COMPUTER",
  "brand": "Test",
  "model": "Test",
  "purchaseDate": "2024-01-15T00:00:00.000Z",
  "warrantyExpiry": "2027-01-15T00:00:00.000Z",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "storeId": 1
}

# Expected: 403 Forbidden ❌
# {
#   "statusCode": 403,
#   "message": "Forbidden resource",
#   "error": "Forbidden"
# }

### ===============================================
### STEP 7: SUPER_ADMIN Update Equipment (Should Fail ❌)
### ===============================================
PUT {{baseUrl}}/equipment/1
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenSuperAdmin}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Super Admin Should Not Update"
}

# Expected: 403 Forbidden ❌

### ===============================================
### STEP 8: SUPER_ADMIN Delete Equipment (Should Fail ❌)
### ===============================================
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/equipment/1
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenSuperAdmin}}

# Expected: 403 Forbidden ❌

### ===============================================
### STEP 9: Login as Help Desk (For Comparison)
### ===============================================
POST {{apiBase}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "helpdesk@rim.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

# Copy access_token และใส่ใน @tokenHelpDesk

### ===============================================
### STEP 10: HELP_DESK Create Equipment (Should Success ✅)
### ===============================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/equipment
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenHelpDesk}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serialNumber": "SN-HELPDESK-SUCCESS",
  "name": "Help Desk Can Create",
  "category": "COMPUTER",
  "brand": "Dell",
  "model": "Test Model",
  "purchaseDate": "2024-01-15T00:00:00.000Z",
  "warrantyExpiry": "2027-01-15T00:00:00.000Z",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "storeId": 1
}

# Expected: 201 Created ✅
# แสดงว่า HELP_DESK สามารถสร้างได้

# =========================================================
# Expected Results Summary
# =========================================================

# ✅ SUPER_ADMIN CAN:
# - View Equipment (GET)           → 200 OK
# - View Equipment by ID (GET)     → 200 OK
# - View Statistics (GET)          → 200 OK
# - View Logs (GET)                → 200 OK

# ❌ SUPER_ADMIN CANNOT:
# - Create Equipment (POST)        → 403 Forbidden
# - Update Equipment (PUT)         → 403 Forbidden
# - Delete Equipment (DELETE)      → 403 Forbidden

# ✅ HELP_DESK CAN:
# - All of the above +
# - Create Equipment (POST)        → 201 Created
# - Update Equipment (PUT)         → 200 OK
# - Delete Equipment (DELETE)      → 200 OK

# =========================================================
# Permissions Matrix (SRS v3.10.1 Compliant)
# =========================================================

# | Operation | SUPER_ADMIN | IT_MANAGER | HELP_DESK | TECHNICIAN | END_USER |
# |-----------|-------------|------------|-----------|------------|----------|
# | View      | ✅          | ✅         | ✅        | ✅         | ✅       |
# | Create    | ❌          | ❌         | ✅        | ❌         | ❌       |
# | Update    | ❌          | ❌         | ✅        | ❌         | ❌       |
# | Delete    | ❌          | ❌         | ✅        | ❌         | ❌       |

# =========================================================
# Notes
# =========================================================

# 1. ตาม SRS v3.10.1:
#    - SUPER_ADMIN: ตั้งค่าระบบ + ดูรายงานทั้งหมด เท่านั้น
#    - IT_MANAGER: จัดการ User + Reassign งาน + ดูรายงาน
#    - HELP_DESK: Gate Keeper - CRUD Incident/Store/Equipment ได้ทั้งหมด
#    - SUPERVISOR: มอบหมายงาน + Reassign งาน
#    - TECHNICIAN: รับงาน + ซ่อม

# 2. ถ้า SUPER_ADMIN หรือ IT_MANAGER ต้องการ CRUD:
#    → ต้องเพิ่ม Role HELP_DESK (Multi-role system)

# 3. การแยก Role ชัดเจนตาม SRS:
#    - Admin (Configuration)     ← SUPER_ADMIN
#    - Operations (CRUD)         ← HELP_DESK
#    - Management (Oversight)    ← IT_MANAGER
#    - Execution (Field Work)    ← TECHNICIAN

# =========================================================
# Why SUPER_ADMIN Cannot CRUD?
# =========================================================

# 1. Separation of Duties (แยกหน้าที่ชัดเจน)
#    - Admin ≠ Operations
#    - ป้องกันการใช้สิทธิ์ที่มากเกินไป

# 2. Security (ความปลอดภัย)
#    - Admin ไม่ควรแก้ไขข้อมูลปฏิบัติการโดยตรง
#    - Audit Trail ชัดเจน

# 3. Best Practice (แนวปฏิบัติที่ดี)
#    - Admin จัดการระบบ
#    - Operations จัดการข้อมูล
#    - ไม่ผสมกัน

# 4. Real-world Example:
#    - Database Admin ≠ Application User
#    - System Admin ≠ Content Editor
#    - Root User ≠ Service User

# =========================================================
# Multi-Role Solution
# =========================================================

# ถ้า SUPER_ADMIN ต้องการ CRUD (เฉพาะกรณีจำเป็น):

# 1. เพิ่ม Role HELP_DESK:
### Add HELP_DESK role to SUPER_ADMIN
POST {{apiBase}}/users/:id/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenSuperAdmin}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "HELP_DESK"
}

# 2. Logout และ Login ใหม่
POST {{apiBase}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "superadmin@rim.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

# 3. ตอนนี้ SUPER_ADMIN จะมี roles: ["SUPER_ADMIN", "HELP_DESK"]
#    - ✅ สามารถ CRUD ได้ทั้งหมด
#    - ✅ ยังคงมีสิทธิ์ Admin อยู่
#    - ✅ Audit Trail จะบันทึกว่าใช้ role ไหน

# =========================================================
# Testing Checklist
# =========================================================

# □ Login as SUPER_ADMIN
# □ View Equipment → 200 OK ✅
# □ View by ID → 200 OK ✅
# □ View Statistics → 200 OK ✅
# □ View Logs → 200 OK ✅
# □ Create Equipment → 403 Forbidden ❌
# □ Update Equipment → 403 Forbidden ❌
# □ Delete Equipment → 403 Forbidden ❌
# □ Login as HELP_DESK
# □ Create Equipment → 201 Created ✅

